  "commit_message": "[XLA:CPU] Robust submodule stitching in HloModuleStitcher.\n\nImprove HloModuleStitcher to be safer and more efficient:\n- Implement circular dependency detection to prevent stack overflow, returning an InternalError if a cycle is detected.\n- Implement redundant recursive call avoidance using a visited modules cache to optimize stitching in complex graphs (e.g., diamond dependencies).\n- Ensure pass reusability by resetting the visited cache on top-level entry before any checks.\n- Add comprehensive ",
